    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been a fantastic companion and is still in really solid shape. It runs beautifully and has been well-maintained, so you can drive off with total peace of mind. There are a few tiny signs of use, but honestly, it still looks great and feels even better behind the wheel! It's the perfect mix of reliable and fun\u2014come see for yourself and take it for a spin! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 33800.0,
