      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine. This example has been meticulously maintained with a focus on structural and internal longevity; the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The high-pressure individual throttle bodies provide sharp atmospheric response, paired with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior displays minor patina consistent with enthusiastic road use, the chassis dynamics remain sharp due to refreshed control arm bushings and a functional M-variable differential lock. A true driver\u2019s specification optimized for performance and reliability.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Reliable runner. Clean title.",
      "price": 31500.0,
