    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, offering a balanced blend of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a lustrous finish that catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use like small stone chips. Step inside to find an inviting cabin where the upholstery remains firm and clean, and every feature\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, reflecting a consistent maintenance schedule. It handles with precision and stops confidently, providing a driving experience that feels tight and responsive. This car has been a reliable companion, kept in a smoke-free environment and garage-stored when not in use. It is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence, needing nothing but a new destination.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
