    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies both mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our dealership's exacting standards for performance and safety. Featuring a well-appointed interior and a robust powertrain, the vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience and remains in commendable condition throughout. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile that perfectly balances enduring value with dependable service.",
      "price": 36500.0,
