    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty, and it has been so reliable for me over the years! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained, so it's totally ready for its next adventure. It runs like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway. I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
