    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary structural concerns. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides precise engagement, delivering power through the factory variable M differential. The suspension retains its original geometry with recently refreshed bushings, ensuring the sharp turn-in and neutral handling characteristics synonymous with the chassis. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) and 8,000 RPM redline remain uncompromising. A true driver\u2019s example with a clean title and documented service history.",
